data.description: Looking for savings? Check out this beautiful move-in ready, solar powered, 3 bedroom, 2 bath home! This lovely home features an open concept kitchen with stainless steel appliances, gas stove, newer cabinets and countertops. Get cozy in the living room in front of the fireplace. Original Hardwood floor and lots of natural light. Large bonus room that can be used as extra living or in home office. Newer electrical panel, heat pump, windows, skylight, sun tubes, roof and solar panels. All of this plus this home sits on a huge lot that is conveniently located for shopping, JBLM, Lake Steilacoom, and I-5
